summary: This is a racemenu preset of one of my own characters. I've had a lot of requests for this so here it is :)
descriptionHtml:
[font=Times New Roman][size=4]This is a racemenu preset of one of my own characters. I've had a lot of requests for this so here it is :)

I uploaded two versions. The first is the one which is the one which can be seen in my bodyslide preset mod. The second is an updated version which uses different eyes and slightly modified features. I like the updated version better but left the original on for the people who requested it.

The preset is designed for a nord female.

[color=#980000]~REQUIREMENTS~[/color]
- [color=#1e84cc]Racemenu[/color]
-[color=#1e84cc]RAN's Type D headmesh [/color](you can use it without if you really must, but the nose will be too wide so you'll have to edit that yourself)
-[color=#1e84cc]KS Hairdos- Renewal[/color]
-[color=#1e84cc]Eyes of Aber[/color] (for original version)
-[color=#1e84cc]Cat Like Eyes[/color] (for updated version)
-[color=#1e84cc]Brows[/color]
-[color=#1e84cc]The Neith Team Warpaints Set[/color] (this is probably the most subtle feature, but it looks nicer if you use it)

[color=#ff7700]~RECOMMENDED~[/color]
-[color=#1e84cc]Pride of Valhalla CBBE [/color](if you want matching skin)
-[color=#1e84cc]Dark Sorceress Bodyslide Preset[/color] (my own preset if you want the body to look exactly the same)

Feel free to put your own screenshots of her in the images section :D

Check out my bodyslide preset here: https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/83216/?

I hope you all enjoy
[color=#ff0000]~Syvanna[/color][/size][/font]
author: Syvanna
